Package: ExpressOM
Type: Package
Title: Expression Overview and Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Author: TL
Maintainer: TL <lavauxt@gmail.com>
Description: A fully modularized R package for bulk RNA-seq analysis, wrapping
    tximport, DESeq2, clusterProfiler, SPIA, fgsea, ReactomePA, DOSE and Enrichr
    into a streamlined, automated workflow. Also supports isoform-level analysis
    with DTE/DTU (DRIMSeq and complementary DEXSeq engines) and
    IsoformSwitchAnalyzeR, including enhanced graphic interpretation via
    isoform switch summary plots, sashimi-style junction usage diagrams, and
    exon-bin usage comparison plots.
